      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_d6dc66e5cca34cf283171f00385ef1bf">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Center for Language Study (CLIS) was established at Yale in 1999. The Language Laboratory, which had been administratively under Information Technology Services, became part of the center in the same year.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_a2c8de714cbe71827563a4e5b1e71d52">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of a 1979 report to the provost and annual reports of the Yale Language Laboratory.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
